{"title":"Linear Algebra","date":"2018-10-19T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 20, 2018","L":"10/20/2018","MM-DD":"10-20"},"link":"2018/10/20/Linear Algebra","tags":["Machine Learning"],"categories":["Machine Learning"],"updated":"2020-02-09T08:37:19.000Z","content":"<h4 id=\"矩阵和向量\">矩阵和向量<a href=\"#矩阵和向量\" title=\"矩阵和向量\"></a></h4><p><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image37.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"><br> 矩阵的维数即行数x列数<br> Aij指第i行第j列。<br> 向量是一种特殊的矩阵，列向量<img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image37.2.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"加法和标量乘法\">加法和标量乘法<a href=\"#加法和标量乘法\" title=\"加法和标量乘法\"></a></h4><ol><li>矩阵的加法：行列数相等的可以加。<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image38.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"></li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法：每个元素都要乘。<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image38.2.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"矩阵向量乘法\">矩阵向量乘法<a href=\"#矩阵向量乘法\" title=\"矩阵向量乘法\"></a></h4>矩阵和向量的乘法如图：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image39.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"矩阵乘法\">矩阵乘法<a href=\"#矩阵乘法\" title=\"矩阵乘法\"></a></h4></li>\n<li>m x n 矩阵乘于n x o 矩阵，变成m x o 矩阵。<br>如下两个矩阵A，B ：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image40.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"乘法的性质\">乘法的性质<a href=\"#乘法的性质\" title=\"乘法的性质\"></a></h4></li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法不满足交换律</li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法满足结合律</li>\n<li>单位矩阵：从左上角到右下角的主对角线上的元素都为1其他全是0, 表示为I或E</li>\n<li>AA-1 = A-1A=I</li>\n<li>AI = IA = A<h4 id=\"矩阵的逆，转置\">矩阵的逆，转置<a href=\"#矩阵的逆，转置\" title=\"矩阵的逆，转置\"></a></h4></li>\n<li>矩阵的逆：如果矩阵A（m * m）有逆矩阵则：AA-1=A-1A=I</li>\n<li>转置：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image42.PNG?raw=true\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"image\"></li>\n<li>矩阵的转置基本性质:<br>(𝐴 ± 𝐵)𝑇 = 𝐴𝑇 ± 𝐵𝑇<br>(𝐴 × 𝐵)𝑇 = 𝐵𝑇 × 𝐴𝑇<br>(𝐴𝑇)𝑇 = 𝐴<br>(KA)T = KAT</li>\n</ol>","prev":{"title":"Regularization","link":"2018/11/10/Regularization"},"next":{"title":"Linear Regression Multiple","link":"2018/10/15/Linear Regression Multiple"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2018/10/20/Linear Algebra/"}